# CODEOWNERS — Open Internet Reference
#
# GitHub uses this file to auto-assign reviewers on pull requests.
# Each path pattern maps to one or more GitHub users or teams who must
# approve changes before merge (when required reviews are enabled).
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <@owner> [<@owner> ...]
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

